    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Puppet Masters who practice the Green Technique are known as Marionettists. Similar to Puppeteers, these Puppet Masters command one or multiple puppets to cleave their way to victory. But what sets the Green Technique apart is its focus on battlefield control. </p><p>The standard Bukijutsu practice of Puppet Tools is elevated to incorporate more complicated chakra techniques, such as Ninjutsu and Genjutsu, to command the tide of battle, as opposed to controlling a battle with Traps and other Shinobi tools.</p>",
